quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  20,38,"Tuma nde Men lonnginnoo yumma maa…óa ko Men lonngini mo kon; kon ko Alla Reenirmaa …óum immorde e pewje Fir'awna."
  20,39,"Gom…óii Men Yamirii mo fewndo Men Lonnginnoo mo: " [Men Daali] Werlo mo ka hontoore …ìaawo jibineede makko, li…ìaa hontoore nden ka maayo, aray maayo ngon bogoo mo ka fonngo sabu Yamiroore Amen, ∆¥etta mo ga√±o Am e ga√±o makko, on le ko Fir'awna, Mi wa…ói e maa…óa Giggol immorde ka Am, yim…ìe …ìen yi…óumaa, e fii yo a ne'e e ndenka Am e ngaynateeri Am."
  20,40,"Tuma nde banndiraawo maa…óa on yaltunoo himo yaara kala ka hontoore nden yaari himo jokki nde, o wi'ani on ∆¥ittu…óo mo: "Enee yo mi tinndin on e ne'oowo mo muynina ayna mo?" Men Neeminiri e maa…óa artirgol ma ka yumma maa…óa fii yo o weltor artugol maa…óa ka makko, hara o sunaaki fii ma…óa maa…óa. Waru…óaa on qibtiyankoojo mo banti…óaa, Men Neeminiri e maa…óa danndugol ma e lepte …óen, Men la…ì…ìinmaa laawol …ìaawo laawol immorde e kala jarrabuyeeji …ói hawrondir…óaa e mu'un, yaltu…óaa √±ii…ìu…óaa duu…ìi ka yim…ìe Madyana, refti aru…óaa e on waqtu hettanaa…óo ma nde arataa e makko fii yewtidugol e maa…óa an Muusaa."
  20,41,"Mi Su…ìimaa fii yo a wonu Nulaa…óo immorde e Am hi…óa yottina e yim…ìe …ìen ko Mi Wahayini kon e maa…óa."
  20,42,"Yahu -an Muusaa- e musi…ó…óo maa…óa on Haaruuna, wonndude e Aayeeje Amen tinndin…óe …óen e Kattan…óe Alla e ngootimbaaku Makko, wata on lo'ino e noddugol faade e Am, maa…óum e annditugol Lam."
  20,43,"Yahee ka Fir'awna, pellet, kanko o yawtii keerol ngol e keeferaaku ngun e sanndal…óanagol Alla."
  20,44,"Wi'anee mo konngol newiingol, ngol aladaa e √±aadde; tijjagol o waajitoto o hula Alla o tuuba."
  20,45,"Muusaa e Haaruuna (yo …ìe his) maaki: "Menen dey me…óen huli wata o yaccin lepte …óen ko adii [men] timminnde noddugol mo, maa nde o yawtata keerol ngol ka too√±irgol men warngo ngon maa tanaa …óum."
  20,46,"Alla Daalani …ìe: "Wata on hulu; pellet, Min Mi…óo wonndiri e mo'on ballal ngal e semminngol ngol, Mi…óo Nana Mi…óo Yi'a ko woni wa…óude kon hakku- nde moo…óon e makko"."
  20,47,"Aree ka makko, wi'anon mo: "Menen ko men Nulaa…ìe Joomi maa…óa -an Fir'awna- accidu men e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, wata a leptir …ìe warugol …ìi…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe wor…ìe …ìen, e hersinngol rew…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, gom…óii men addanii ma dalil e goongugol amen immorde ka Joomi maa…óa, hoolaare nden e Lepte Alla …óen ko gom…óin…óo jokki Peewal Alla ngal woo …óum woodani."
  20,48,"Menen gom…óii Alla Wahayinii e Amen wonndema Lepte …óen ka aduna e ka Laakara …óe fawike on fennu…óo Aayeeje Alla …óen, o …óuurii e ko Nulaa…ìe …ìen addi kon."
  20,49,"Fir'awna tawi no yeddi ko [Muusaa] addi kon, o wi'i: "Ko hommbo woni Joomi moo…óon, on mo aa∆¥i…óon wonndema himo Nuli on faade e am, ko an yo Muusaa?"
  20,50,"Muusaa maaki: "Joomi amen, ko On Okku…óo kala huunde mbaade mayre e noone mayre hawrondi- ray…óo on e mayre, refti O Fewni tageefooji …óin e ko O Tagani …ói kon fii mu'un."
  20,51,"Fir'awna wi'i: "Ko hon…óun woni alhaali moftaaji adii…ói …óin …óin wonunoo…ói e keeferaaku?""